#Mahjong Points Calculator
This is a custom program that calculates mahjong points earned.

#Installation
To get started with the Mahjong Points Calculator, follow these steps:

##Clone the repository to your local machine:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/mahjong-points-calculator.git
Create a virtual environment to isolate the project's dependencies:

python -m venv venv
Activate the virtual environment:

venv\Scripts\activate.bat  # for Windows
source venv/bin/activate  # for macOS or Linux
Install the dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

#Usage
To use the Mahjong Points Calculator, run the following command:

python lobby.py

Alternatively , you can run the lobby.exe to execute the existing version of the project

#Contributing
If you'd like to contribute to this project, please follow these guidelines:

Fork the repository.
Create a new branch for your feature: git checkout -b my-new-feature
